result.notes:
Counts (in cells per litre) of potentially toxic algal cells for The States of 
Jersey analysed using the Utermohl method with light microscopy. These data 
are from water samples collected from designated shellfish growing areas 
around the coast of Jersey for the period 01/4/2004 - 31/3/2019.
